<div class="its-a-match card hoverable">
  <div class="card-image waves-effect waves-block waves-light">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s6 avatar-user-1" style="padding-top: 10px;">
        <img class="avatar-user circle responsive-img z-depth-2 activator" style="
          width: 150px; height: 150px;
          margin: 1px;
          border: 2px solid grey;
          border-color: #64ffda;
          border-radius: 50%;
          -webkit-border-radius: 500px;
          -moz-border-radius: 500px;"
          src= '<%= cl_image_path @user.profile_picture %>'>

      </div>

      <div class="col s6 avatar-user-1" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 10px;">

      <img class="avatar-user circle responsive-img z-depth-2 activator" style="
        width: 150px; height: 150px;
        margin: 1px;
        border: 2px solid grey;
        border-color: #64ffda;
        border-radius: 50%;
        -webkit-border-radius: 500px;
        -moz-border-radius: 500px;"
        src= '<%= cl_image_path current_user.profile_picture %>'>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-content">
    <span class="card-title activator teal-text text-accent-2">
      <h4 class="teal-text text-accent-2 center-align" style="
        border: 4px solid grey;
        border-color: #64ffda;
        padding: 7%;
        margin-bottom: 20%;">
        A new buddy is waiting for you!
      </h4>

      <i class="material-icons right">more_vert</i>
    </span>

    <p><a href="#">Send a message</a></p>
    <p><a href="#">Continue to swipe</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="card-reveal">
    <span class="card-title grey-text text-darken-4">About Dylan<i class="material-icons right">close</i></span>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Distinctio, quis laboriosam harum odit aut quaerat perspiciatis quos ipsam et voluptatum eligendi, sit amet error voluptatem iusto quasi corrupti laborum. Animi!.</p>
  </div>

</div>
